    ("Cramer's rule gives xᵢ = det(Aᵢ)/det(A) and requires:", ["rank < n", "det(A) ≠ 0", "A is symmetric", "A has all positive entries"], 1, "A must be invertible (det ≠ 0)."),
    ("The row space and null space of A are _____ subspaces of Rⁿ.", ["identical", "orthogonal complements", "parallel", "equal"], 1, "Row(A) ⊥ Null(A) and dim sums to n."),
