    ("The Gram matrix Gᵢⱼ = <vᵢ,vⱼ> is positive semi-definite because:", ["it has real entries", "xᵀGx = ||Σxᵢvᵢ||² ≥ 0", "its trace ≥ 0", "eigenvalues are integers"], 1, "Quadratic form equals a squared norm."),
    ("Stacking three 2×2 matrices vertically gives a matrix of size:", ["6×2", "2×6", "6×6", "2×2"], 0, "3 rows of 2×2 blocks → 6 rows, 2 columns."),
